📍 A Journey of Three Decades — Building Alibag’s Future 

For 30 years, Samira Habitats has been more than a real estate name.
We’ve been curators of dreams — shaping Alibag’s coastal lifestyle with vision, purpose, and passion.

From untouched plots to thoughtfully designed homes, our developments are rooted in trust, timeless aesthetics, and a deep respect for the land.

Today, Alibag is no longer just a weekend escape.
It’s emerging as the next lifestyle and investment hotspot, blending nature, luxury, and long-term growth.

It’s the luxury. It’s the Alibag Life by Samira.

#samirahabitats #alibagrealestate #investinalibaug #coastalliving #thealibaglifebysamira
